        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Addressing Teacher Shortages Act of 2024&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill directs the Department of Education (ED) to establish an Addressing Teacher Shortages Program. Through this program, ED shall award grants for local educational agencies&amp;nbsp;to address teacher shortage challenges. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Specifically, grant funds&amp;nbsp;may be used to establish or expand teaching residency programs, teacher mentor programs, specified recruitment and training programs, and other evidence-based strategies to increase teacher retention and support teachers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
